attempts.sparql_query: PREFIX nas: <http://www.semanticdesktop.org/ontologies/2007/04/18/nas#> SELECT ?certainty WHERE {nas:AAL1102 a nas:Aircraft ; nas:modelCertainty ?certainty . nas:AAL20 a nas:Aircraft ; nas:modelCertainty ?certainty2 . FILTER(?certainty > ?certainty2)}
attempts.query_explanation: This query compares the certainty of model designations for AAL1102 and AAL20. It selects the higher value from the two.
